你能够调用以下的API:
[['HRSystem.get_housing_fund_info', {'name': 'HRSystem.get_housing_fund_info', 'description': 'Get the housing fund contribution ratio and base for an employee.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'employee_id', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'the employee ID'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'contribution_ratio', 'description': 'the contribution ratio of the housing fund.'}, {'name': 'base', 'description': 'the base amount for the housing fund.'}]}], ['CityPolicy.get_housing_loan_policy', {'name': 'CityPolicy.get_housing_loan_policy', 'description': 'Get the housing loan policy for a specific city.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'city', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'the city name'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'max_loan_ratio', 'description': 'the maximum loan ratio allowed.'}, {'name': 'interest_rate', 'description': 'the interest rate for housing loans.'}]}], ['FinancialAdvisor.get_loan_planning_advice', {'name': 'FinancialAdvisor.get_loan_planning_advice', 'description': 'Get advice on personal housing loan planning.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'income', 'type': 'NUMBER', 'description': 'the monthly income.'}, {'name': 'expenses', 'type': 'NUMBER', 'description': 'the monthly expenses.'}, {'name': 'housing_fund_info', 'type': 'DICT', 'description': 'the housing fund information.'}, {'name': 'loan_policy', 'type': 'DICT', 'description': 'the housing loan policy information.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'advice', 'description': 'the advice on loan planning.'}]}], ['LoanCalculator.estimate_loan_cost', {'name': 'LoanCalculator.estimate_loan_cost', 'description': 'Estimate the cost of a housing loan.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'loan_amount', 'type': 'NUMBER', 'description': 'the loan amount.'}, {'name': 'interest_rate', 'type': 'FLOAT', 'description': 'the interest rate.'}, {'name': 'loan_term', 'type': 'NUMBER', 'description': 'the loan term in years.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'monthly_payment', 'description': 'the estimated monthly payment.'}, {'name': 'total_interest', 'description': 'the total interest paid over the loan term.'}]}]]
请生成一个解决用户问题的计划，计划应该是一个行为列表，每个行为的格式如下:

[{
    // 动作的ID
    "id": number;
    // 动作要调用的API名称
    "name": string;
    // 当前API的参数输入(JSON格式)
    "args": "str(Record<string, any>)";
}, ...
]

你可以在计划中想象参数的值，这些指令将按顺序执行。
例如，如果你想调用 `api1` 并传入 `arg1` 和 `arg2`，你可以写下面的计划:

[{
    "id": 0,
    "name": "api1",
    "args": "{'arg1': 'value1', 'arg2': 'value2', ...}",
}, ...
]

这些参数将在执行时被替换为真实的值。请注意，参数应该是一个字符串，而不是一个字典。
请在字典的参数中使用 ''，在其他地方使用 ""，不要打印值为 None 或 null 的参数。

你应该只生成一个 JSON 格式的计划列表。列表应该是完整的计划列表，不要有 `...`。
不要生成任何解释 JSON 的文本。
